  "description": "Remove Text Shadows from Hero Section and Update Text Colors\n\nUpdate the hero section typography to improve readability by removing text shadows from headings and adjusting paragraph text color.\n\nRequirements:\n- Remove all text-shadow CSS properties from <h1>, <h2>, <h3>, etc. elements within the hero section\n- Change <p> element color to white (#ffffff or equivalent) in the hero section\n- Remove any text-shadow properties from <p> elements in the hero section\n- Ensure changes only affect the hero section, not other page areas\n- Verify text remains readable against the hero background\n- Check consistency across different viewport sizes and devices",
